	</div>
	<br/><br/>
	<h3>Load from file</h3>
	<div class="subsection"><p>Load a local StratML file from your computer</p>
	  <div class="line">
	    <form style='border: 0px white; padding: 5px' action='/forms/walt5.pl' method='post' enctype='multipart/form-data'>
	      Local StratML <b>File</b>: 
	    <input type='file' name='f' accept='.xml'/>
	    <b> </b>
	    <input style='font-size: 80%' type='submit' value='Import StratML From File'/>
